HEADWORD: Conjector
<hw>Con*ject"or</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.]</ety>
<def>One who guesses or conjectures.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A great <qex>conjector</qex> at other men by their writings.</q>
